### **🖥 Edge Hardware: Processing Power Beyond the Cloud**

✅ **Qualcomm RB3 Gen 2** – Optimized for AI inference on **low-power devices**.  
✅ **Google Coral Edge TPU** – Accelerated machine learning for **IoT and embedded AI**.  
✅ **NVIDIA Jetson** – AI computing for robotics and industrial automation.  
✅ **Apple Neural Engine (ANE)** – AI computations directly on iPhones & iPads.

⚠️ **Ethical Risk:** Proprietary AI hardware **limits accessibility** and enforces **Big Tech monopolies over AI infrastructure**.

**Related Notes:** [[ai-ml-hardware-ai-integration]] | [[ai-infrastructure-equity]]

---

### **🔬 The Future of Decentralized AI**

✅ **Federated Learning** – AI models trained directly on **edge devices**, reducing the need for centralized data collection.  
✅ **TinyML** – AI models optimized for **low-power microcontrollers**.  
✅ **Blockchain + AI** – Distributed AI frameworks for **secure, tamper-proof decision-making**.

⚠️ **Ethical Risk:** Decentralized AI could still replicate **biased patterns** if trained on flawed datasets.

